msgstr "Titre de l'espace"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:961
msgid "Tokens: {space_name}, {site_name}"
msgstr "Jetons : {space_name}, {site_name}"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:970
msgid "Structured Data & Indexing"
msgstr "Données structurées et indexation"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:971
msgid "Schema markup, sitemap inclusion, and noindex rules."
msgstr "Balisage du schéma, inclusion du sitemap et règles noindex."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:975
msgid "Schema Markup"
msgstr "Balisage du schéma"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:979
msgid "Enable DiscussionForumPosting schema on post pages"
msgstr "Active le schéma DiscussionForumPosting sur les pages de messages"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:984
msgid "XML Sitemap"
msgstr "Plan du site XML"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:988
msgid "Include community pages in the WordPress XML sitemap"
msgstr "Inclure les pages communautaires dans le plan du site XML de WordPress"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:993
msgid "Noindex"
msgstr "Noindex"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:998
msgid "Noindex user profile pages"
msgstr "Noindex les pages de profil utilisateur"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1003
msgid "Noindex search result pages"
msgstr "Noindex les pages de résultats de recherche"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1006
msgid ""
"Moderation queues, composer pages, notifications, edit profile, and invite "
"landings always emit noindex (administrative or personal views, not for "
"search results)."
msgstr ""
"Les files de modération, les pages de rédaction, les notifications, la "
"modification du profil et les pages de destination des invitations émettent "
"toujours noindex (vues administratives ou personnelles, non destinées aux "
"résultats de recherche)."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1010
msgid "Twitter / X handle"
msgstr "Identifiant Twitter / X"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1013
msgid ""
"Site handle emitted as twitter:site on every public route. Leave blank to "
"omit."
msgstr ""
"Identifiant du site émis comme twitter:site sur chaque route publique. "
"Laisse vide pour omettre."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1017
msgid "Default share image"
msgstr "Image de partage par défaut"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1020
msgid ""
"og:image URL when a route has no image of its own. Falls back to the "
"WordPress site logo / icon when this is empty."
msgstr ""
"URL og:image quand une route n'a pas sa propre image. Se replie sur le logo "
"/ l'icône du site WordPress quand celui-ci est vide."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1024
msgid "Verify SEO"
msgstr "Vérifier le SEO"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1027
msgid "Open XML sitemap"
msgstr "Ouvre le plan du site XML"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1029
msgid ""
"Confirms /wp-sitemap.xml is reachable and that community URLs (spaces + "
"posts) are listed. New spaces can take a few minutes to appear after the "
"next ping."
msgstr ""
"Confirme que /wp-sitemap.xml est accessible et que les URL communautaires "
"(espaces + messages) sont listées. Les nouveaux espaces peuvent prendre "
"quelques minutes pour apparaître après le prochain ping."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1038
msgid "Social Embeds (Instagram & Facebook)"
msgstr "Intégrations sociales (Instagram & Facebook)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1040
msgid ""
"YouTube, Vimeo, TikTok, Twitter/X, Spotify, SoundCloud, and TED Talks embed "
"automatically with no setup required. Instagram and Facebook require a free "
"Meta Developer App because Meta deprecated anonymous oEmbed access in "
"October 2020."
msgstr ""
"YouTube, Vimeo, TikTok, Twitter/X, Spotify, SoundCloud et TED Talks "
"s'intègrent automatiquement sans configuration requise. Instagram et "
"Facebook nécessitent une application Meta Developer gratuite car Meta a "
"arrêté l'accès oEmbed anonyme en octobre 2020."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1045
msgid "Facebook App ID"
msgstr "ID App Facebook"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1048
msgid "Numeric App ID from your Meta Developer dashboard."
msgstr "ID App numérique de ton tableau de bord Meta Developer."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1052
msgid "Facebook App Secret"
msgstr "Clé secrète App Facebook"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1055
msgid "Secret is stored in wp_options and never exposed to the frontend."
msgstr "La clé secrète est stockée dans wp_options et jamais exposée au frontend."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1062
msgid "How to create a Facebook App (5 minutes, free)"
msgstr "Comment créer une application Facebook (5 minutes, gratuit)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1069
#. translators: 1: developers.facebook.com URL, 2: Create App button label
msgid ""
"Go to %1$s and log in with a Facebook account. Click %2$s in the top-right "
"corner."
msgstr ""
"Va à %1$s et connecte-toi avec un compte Facebook. Clique sur %2$s dans le "
"coin supérieur droit."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1071
msgid "Create App"
msgstr "Créer une application"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1079
#. translators: 1: "Other" use-case label, 2: "Business" app type label
msgid ""
"When asked \"What do you want your app to do?\", pick %1$s. When asked for "
"the app type, pick %2$s. Name it anything, e.g. \"My Forum Embeds\"."
msgstr ""
"Quand on te demande « Que veux-tu que ton application fasse ? », choisis "
"%1$s. Quand on te demande le type d'application, choisis %2$s. Nomme-la "
"comme tu le souhaites, par exemple « Mes intégrations de forum »."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1081
msgid "Business"
msgstr "Business"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1089
#. translators: %s: "oEmbed Read" product label
msgid ""
"On the new app's dashboard, find the %s product in the Products list and "
"click Set Up. It's free."
msgstr ""
"Sur le tableau de bord de la nouvelle application, trouve le produit %s "
"dans la liste des produits et clique sur Configurer. C'est gratuit."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1090
msgid "oEmbed Read"
msgstr "Lecture oEmbed"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1098
#. translators: 1: "Settings > Basic" breadcrumb, 2: App ID label, 3: App
#. Secret label
msgid "Open %1$s. Copy the %2$s and %3$s and paste them into the two fields above."
msgstr ""
"Ouvre %1$s. Copie le %2$s et %3$s et colle-les dans les deux champs "
"ci-dessus."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1099
msgid "Settings → Basic"
msgstr "Paramètres → De base"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1100
msgid "App ID"
msgstr "ID App"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1101
msgid "App Secret"
msgstr "Clé secrète App"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1109
#. translators: 1: "App Review > Requests" breadcrumb, 2: "oembed_read"
#. permission name
msgid ""
"Go to %1$s and request the %2$s permission. Meta typically approves in 1–3 "
"business days. Your app stays in Development Mode until approved; embeds "
"will work for the admin who created the app even before approval."
msgstr ""
"Va à %1$s et demande la permission %2$s. Meta approuve généralement en 1–3 "
"jours ouvrables. Ton application reste en mode de développement jusqu'à "
"approbation ; les intégrations fonctionneront pour l'administrateur qui a "
"créé l'application même avant approbation."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1110
msgid "App Review → Requests"
msgstr "Révision de l'application → Demandes"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1116
msgid ""
"Save the settings here. Instagram and Facebook URLs pasted into posts and "
"replies will now unfurl as rich embeds."
msgstr ""
"Enregistre les paramètres ici. Les URL Instagram et Facebook collées dans "
"les messages et réponses se déploieront maintenant en tant qu'intégrations "
"enrichies."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1120
msgid "Privacy note:"
msgstr "Remarque sur la confidentialité :"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1121
msgid ""
"Jetonomy only sends oEmbed requests to Meta when a user pastes an "
"Instagram/Facebook URL. No tracking, no user data: just the public post URL "
"and your app token. Leave these fields blank to skip Instagram/Facebook "
"embeds entirely; the URL will render as a plain clickable link."
msgstr ""
"Jetonomy n'envoie des demandes oEmbed à Meta que lorsqu'un utilisateur "
"colle une URL Instagram/Facebook. Pas de suivi, pas de données utilisateur "
": juste l'URL du message public et ton jeton d'application. Laisse ces "
"champs vides pour ignorer complètement les intégrations Instagram/Facebook "
"; l'URL s'affichera sous la forme d'un lien cliquable simple."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1129
#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1299
msgid "SEO Pro"
msgstr "SEO Pro"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1130
msgid ""
"Open Graph tags, per-space canonical URLs, breadcrumb schema, and advanced "
"robots control."
msgstr ""
"Balises Open Graph, URL canoniques par espace, schéma de fil d'Ariane et "
"contrôle avancé des robots."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1140
msgid "CAPTCHA Provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur CAPTCHA"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1141
msgid ""
"Protect post and reply forms from bots. Trusted members (trust level 2+) "
"are always exempt."
msgstr ""
"Protéger les formulaires de messages et de réponses contre les robots. Les "
"membres de confiance (niveau de confiance 2+) sont toujours exonérés."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1150
msgid ""
"A CAPTCHA provider is selected but the Site Key and/or Secret Key is empty. "
"The CAPTCHA will not render until both keys are filled in."
msgstr ""
"Un fournisseur CAPTCHA est sélectionné mais la clé de site et/ou la clé "
"secrète est vide. Le CAPTCHA ne s'affichera pas tant que les deux clés ne "
"seront pas remplies."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1152
msgid ""
"CAPTCHA keys are saved but the Provider is set to Disabled, so no CAPTCHA "
"renders. Select Cloudflare Turnstile or reCAPTCHA above to activate it."
msgstr ""
"Les clés CAPTCHA sont enregistrées mais le fournisseur est défini sur "
"Désactivé, donc aucun CAPTCHA ne s'affiche. Sélectionne Cloudflare "
"Turnstile ou reCAPTCHA ci-dessus pour l'activer."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1157
msgid "Heads up:"
msgstr "Attention :"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1165
msgid "Provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1168
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Désactivé"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1169
msgid "Google reCAPTCHA v3 (invisible)"
msgstr "Google reCAPTCHA v3 (invisible)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1170
msgid "Cloudflare Turnstile (privacy-friendly)"
msgstr "Cloudflare Turnstile (respectueux de la vie privée)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1175
msgid "Site Key"
msgstr "Clé du site"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1179
msgid "reCAPTCHA: get keys at"
msgstr "reCAPTCHA : obtiens les clés sur"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1181
msgid "Turnstile: get keys at"
msgstr "Turnstile : obtiens les clés sur"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1187
msgid "Secret Key"
msgstr "Clé secrète"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1190
msgid "Stored securely. Never shared with visitors."
msgstr "Stockée de manière sécurisée. Jamais partagée avec les visiteurs."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1194
msgid "Score Threshold"
msgstr "Seuil de score"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1197
msgid ""
"reCAPTCHA v3 only. Scores below this value are treated as bots (0.1 = "
"permissive, 0.9 = strict). Default: 0.5."
msgstr ""
"reCAPTCHA v3 uniquement. Les scores en dessous de cette valeur sont traités "
"comme des bots (0,1 = permissif, 0,9 = strict). Par défaut : 0,5."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1208
msgid "Unlock 13 Pro Extensions"
msgstr "Déverrouille 13 extensions Pro"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1210
msgid ""
"Your community is growing. Give it reactions, messaging, polls, analytics, "
"badges, webhooks, and more. Each feature is an independent module you "
"enable only when you need it."
msgstr ""
"Ta communauté grandit. Donne-lui des réactions, des messages, des sondages, "
"des analyses, des badges, des webhooks, et bien plus. Chaque fonctionnalité "
"est un module indépendant que tu actives seulement quand tu en as besoin."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1213
msgid "Get Jetonomy Pro. Starting at $69/yr."
msgstr "Obtiens Jetonomy Pro. À partir de 69 $/an."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1218
#. translators: %s: coupon code
msgid "Use code %s for 30%% off lifetime plans."
msgstr "Utilise le code %s pour 30 %% de réduction sur les forfaits à vie."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1227
msgid "Pro Extensions"
msgstr "Extensions Pro"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1228
msgid ""
"Each extension is independent. Enable only what you need. Disabled "
"extensions load zero code."
msgstr ""
"Chaque extension est indépendante. Active seulement ce dont tu as besoin. "
"Les extensions désactivées ne chargent aucun code."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1233
msgid "Emoji Reactions"
msgstr "Réactions avec emoji"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1235
msgid "Like, love, and celebrate with Slack-style reactions on posts and replies."
msgstr ""
"Aime, adore et célèbre avec des réactions de style Slack sur les messages "
"et les réponses."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1239
msgid "Private Messaging"
msgstr "Messages privés"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1241
msgid "One-on-one and group conversations between community members."
msgstr "Conversations individuelles et de groupe entre les membres de la communauté."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1245
msgid "Polls"
msgstr "Sondages"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1247
msgid "Create polls within posts for community voting and decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Crée des sondages dans les messages pour les votes et la prise de décision "
"de la communauté."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1251
msgid "Analytics Dashboard"
msgstr "Tableau de bord Analytics"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1253
msgid "Engagement graphs, user growth, top spaces, post trends, and CSV export."
msgstr ""
"Graphiques d'engagement, croissance des utilisateurs, top des espaces, "
"tendances des messages et export CSV."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1257
msgid "Email Digests"
msgstr "Résumés par email"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1259
msgid "Daily and weekly email digests of community activity for subscribed users."
msgstr ""
"Résumés quotidiens et hebdomadaires par email de l'activité de la "
"communauté pour les utilisateurs abonnés."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1263
msgid "Web Push"
msgstr "Web Push"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1265
msgid "Browser push notifications for replies, mentions, and forum events."
msgstr ""
"Notifications push du navigateur pour les réponses, mentions et événements "
"du forum."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1269
msgid "Webhooks"
msgstr "Webhooks"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1271
msgid ""
"Fire HTTP POST requests to Zapier, Slack, n8n, or any endpoint on forum "
"events."
msgstr ""
"Envoie des requêtes HTTP POST à Zapier, Slack, n8n ou n'importe quel "
"endpoint lors d'événements du forum."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1275
msgid "Reply by Email"
msgstr "Répondre par email"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1277
msgid "Members reply to notifications by email. No login required."
msgstr "Les membres répondent aux notifications par email. Aucune connexion requise."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1281
msgid "Custom Badges"
msgstr "Badges personnalisés"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1283
msgid "Create and auto-award custom badges based on community activity criteria."
msgstr ""
"Crée et attribue automatiquement des badges personnalisés en fonction des "
"critères d'activité de la communauté."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1287
#: includes/admin/views/space-edit.php:47
msgid "Custom Fields"
msgstr "Champs personnalisés"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1289
msgid ""
"Add custom fields to posts and user profiles: text, select, checkbox, date, "
